\paragraph{Dice game.}

Roll this many dice based on how old you are:

\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{|c|c|}
\hline
  {\bf Age} & {\bf \#Dice} \\
  \hline
  4 years old & 2 or more dice \\
  \hline
  6 years old & 3 or more dice \\
  \hline
  8 years old & 4 or more dice \\
  \hline
\end{tabular}
\end{center}

Write down the total number of dots from each roll.

